    <body>
      <div type="book">
        <linkGrp type="notes"/>
        <div n="949A703C">
          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-949A703C-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-949A703C-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-949A703C-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">A French Gentleman dining with some Company on a Fast Day, call'd for some Bacon and Eggs: The rest were very angry, and reprov'd him for so heinous a sin. Whereupon he writ the following lines extempore.&#13;</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-949A703C-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-949A703C-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-949A703C-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-949A703C-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-949A703C-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-949A703C-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-949A703C-line-1" n="1">Peut on croire avec bon sens</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-949A703C-line-2" n="2">Qu'un lardon le mit en colere;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-949A703C-line-3" n="3">Ou, que manger un Harang</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-949A703C-line-4" n="4">C'est un Secret pour luy plaire?</l>
            <l rend="indent(2)" xml:id="swift-949A703C-line-5" n="5">|En sa gloire evelopè</l>
            <l rend="indent(2)" xml:id="swift-949A703C-line-6" n="6">|Songet'il bien de nos Soupé.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-949A703C-line-7" n="7"><lb/>In English by Dean Swift__Who can believe with common Sense,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-949A703C-line-8" n="8">A Bacon-Slice gives God Offence!</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-949A703C-line-9" n="9">Or, how a Herring hath a Charm</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-949A703C-line-10" n="10">Almighty Anger to disarm?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-949A703C-line-11" n="11">Wrapt up in Majesty divine,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-949A703C-line-12" n="12">Does he regard on what we dine?</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
